{"word":"νωλεμές","slug":"νωλεμές","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<entryFree id=\"n71382\" key=\"nwleme/s\" type=\"main\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"entryFree\"> <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">νωλεμές</orth>, <pos opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"pos\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Adv.\">Adv.</a></pos> <sense id=\"n71382.0\" n=\"A\" level=\"1\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">without pause, unceasingly,</tr_> <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ν. αἰεί</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:9:317\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Il.\">Il.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">9.317</biblScope></bibl></cit>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:17:385\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">17.385</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg002.perseus-grc1:16:191\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Od.\">Od.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">16.191</biblScope></bibl>, etc. ; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">οἱ δ᾽ αἰεὶ . . ν. ἐγχρίμπτοντο</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:17:413\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Il.\">Il.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">17.413</biblScope> </bibl> </cit> : without <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">αἰεί, μάχην ἀλίαστον ἔχουσι ν.</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:14:58\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">14.58</biblScope> </bibl> </cit> ; later, <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">firmly,</tr_> <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ν. ἐρρίζωθεν</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0001.tlg001.perseus-grc1:2:605\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ A.R.\">A.R.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">2.605</biblScope> </bibl> </cit> :—also <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">νωλεμέως</orth>, <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">πόνον τ᾽ ἐχέμεν καὶ ὀϊζὺν ν.</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:13:3\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Il.\">Il.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">13.3</biblScope> </bibl> </cit> ; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ν. ἐχέμεν</quote_> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">persevere,</tr_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:5:492\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">5.492</biblScope> </bibl> </cit> ; but <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ν. κτείνοντο</foreign> they were murdered <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">without pause,</tr_> i.e. one after the other, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg002.perseus-grc1:11:413\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Od.\">Od.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">11.413</biblScope></bibl>.—<gramGrp opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gramGrp\"> <gram type=\"dialect\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gram\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Ep.\">Ep.</a></gram> </gramGrp> word, used by <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0266.tlg001:5:5\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Tyrt.</author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">5.5</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0266.tlg001:12:17\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">12.17</biblScope></bibl>.</sense> </entryFree>"}]}